Theorem (3.75) “ex falso quodlibet”: false ⇒ p
Proof:
    false ⇒ p
  =⟨ “Material implication”⟩
    ¬ false ∨ p
  =⟨ “Negation of `false`”⟩
    true ∨ p
  =⟨ “Zero of ∨”⟩
    true

