Theorem (3.78) “Case analysis”: (p ⇒ r) ∧ (q ⇒ r) ≡ (p ∨ q ⇒ r)
Proof:
    p ∨ q ⇒ r
  =⟨ “Material implication”⟩
    ¬ (p ∨ q) ∨ r
  =⟨ “De Morgan”⟩
    (¬ p ∧ ¬ q) ∨ r
  =⟨ “Distributivity of ∨ over ∧”⟩
    (¬ p ∨ r) ∧ (¬ q ∨ r)
  =⟨ “Material implication”⟩
    (p ⇒ r) ∧ (q ⇒ r)

